tool.name: NRT_Visualise_Areas

param.name: in_feat
param.dialogReference:
Monitoring area feature class that holds one or more monitoring areas created prior using the Create Monitoring Areas tool.

Note: This feature is expected to be named "monitoring_areas". Any input that does not contain the correct structure created by the Create Project tool will be rejected.

param.name: in_set_area
param.displayname: Select the monitoring area to modify
param.dialogReference: The specific monitoring area within the input feature in which to generate density layers.

param.name: out_nc
param.dialogReference: An output NetCDF holding several variables representing different monitoring area vegetation and change density variables.

tool.summary:
Visualise various vegetation and change density layers for a specified monitoring area. These density layers include:

- veg_avg_all_time: Average vegetation from start of pre-imapct training period to now

- veg_std_all_time: Standard deviation of vegetation from start of pre-imapct training period to now

- veg_latest_time: Vegetation at most recent date

- change_max_all_time_incline: Maximum change deviation in upwards direction (incline) from start of pre-impact training period to now

- change_max_all_time_decline: Maximum change deviation in downwards direction (decline) from start of pre-impact training period to now

- change_avg_all_time_incline: Average change deviation in upwards direction (incline) from start of pre-impact training period to now

- change_avg_all_time_decline: Average change deviation in downwards direction (decline) from start of pre-impact training period to now

- change_latest_time_incline: Latest change deviation in upwards direction (incline)

- change_latest_time_decline: Latest change deviation in downwards direction (decline)

- alerts_cnt_all_time_incline: Total number of alerts triggered in upwards direction (incline) from start of pre-impact training period to now

- alerts_cnt_all_time_decline: Total number of alerts triggered in downwards direction (decline) from start of pre-impact training period to now
